If you could make a change to anything you've written over the years, what would it be?

In The Dispossessed, I would mention the
communal pickle barrels at street corners in
the big towns, restocked by whoever in the
community has made or kept more pickles
than they need. I knew about the free
pickles all along, but never could fit them
into the book.
